str-setup:
Welcome to the guild configuration wizard!

I will guide you through the configuration. You can always re-run this setup or manually change the settings so do not worry if you don't do everything like you wanted.

That being said, let's start the wizard! Note that the changes will apply only if you confirm them after the wizard finishes. If you make a mistake, let the command to timeout and start over.
